          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/heymynameisrob" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-fit px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm bg-gray-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-center font-medium hover:bg-gray-4 focus">
